,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:33:59.000Z","msg":"見到佢眼濕濕，眼都紅曬個陣我心都軟埋。即刻攬返實佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4485dfa28cf049df6673bdf8724ebb926bf90215","tid":42273,"uid":66252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:41:21.000Z","msg":"好少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢話因為喊都解決唔到問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e48a9fea702ad49397550c2b728e5258a32f42f","tid":42273,"uid":66625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:49:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>見到佢攬住我成個小朋友咁 喊到好崩潰 覺得好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想知佢因咩事喊成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為一啲野 我忍唔住係佢面前喊 我本身好易喊所以喊左好多次 佢覺得係佢做得唔夠好所以傷害到我"},{"pid":"1f236a99fe23aeb32fe8960db56482816a45cb63","tid":42273,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:51:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有病睇下好<br />\n下下界手個個都難受"},{"pid":"f39607508c170d6ea692cc5e1e6fbf985838cc85","tid":42273,"uid":66625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:51:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>見到佢攬住我成個小朋友咁 喊到好崩潰 覺得好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想知佢因咩事喊成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為一啲野 我忍唔住係佢面前喊 我本身好易喊所以喊左好多次 佢覺得係佢做得唔夠好所以傷害到我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係佢初戀 佢唔係好識點同女仔相處 平時好多野都好似冇乜感覺咁 點知佢無啦啦係我面前喊果下真係好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d310dd435cc26b4491f1cf8b5402916949d185","tid":42273,"uid":21544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:03:49.000Z","msg":"同男朋友longd 明明去機場個時都無事 但到機場坐左係到佢就攬住我流左眼淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後尾真係入閘 佢就喊住又笑咁話入閘啦 排緊隊個時擰轉面望左一眼見到佢隻眼紅曬咁望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61cf07460d66c9425d33ce43a9d2b8d3d0cdb62f","tid":42273,"uid":22820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:04:48.000Z","msg":"鬧交鬧到差d分手個陣試過"},{"pid":"d1a2732ad619f0ce3c5f9468ec57b519b3baef58","tid":42273,"uid":55570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:16:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我聽過有條仔因為條女唔俾搞就係佢面前喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依個好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"904c2d17f0079a6cf410acd258cee412c6a782cc","tid":42273,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:18:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>喊又點 係佢面前喊佢都已經冇感覺了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n女人絕起上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n羅定偉？"},{"pid":"ec6aad7a484d7a31e018a7c997c9086d106c9eed","tid":42273,"uid":9517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:29:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>西面西到佢喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9a1361d15e5a1cfb39d2e9bf539ebfd0d1b0c99","tid":42273,"uid":30552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T17:02:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我已經唔再識得喊，其實好可悲。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我男友都係，佢話自從唔係細路仔之後就唔識得喊，係好唔開心都喊唔出。我知佢童年唔係過得好開心，可能係咁影響咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026de6e4b206dd14d486cb64a52c3c1e32b7722c","tid":42273,"uid":24041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T17:09:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我已經唔再識得喊，其實好可悲。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我男友都係，佢話自從唔係細路仔之後就唔識得喊，係好唔開心都喊唔出。我知佢童年唔係過得好開心，可能係咁影響咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係，人愈大好似愈冷咁。唔開心都係訓完就算，喊唔出"},{"pid":"73b3295fb3fa8367430da92f898249ff456fe53f","tid":42273,"uid":13768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T17:14:02.000Z","msg":"生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df3c20bb51488943ebd15a2b07f244b47fdac57","tid":42273,"uid":14514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T17:18:09.000Z","msg":"喊到狗咁 之後佢走撚左block埋我啲野 之後同條新仔開心生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  以後都唔敢信女人"},{"pid":"922abfbd658a29e02bdfe089caede9bc35282ad6","tid":42273,"uid":7204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T17:23:21.000Z","msg":"同ex longd 次次分開都有喊 有好幾次都係因為收到份佢覺得好窩心既禮物所以喊<br />\n<br />\n現任果陣係聽到我同ex d野嬲到眼紅紅就喊就喊咁<br />\n<br />\nBtw其實我覺得有本事感動到男朋友都係一件好值得自豪既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c86980b837ee5fe4ee93ca500ae485939a58146","tid":42273,"uid":26749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T17:45:40.000Z","msg":"你喊住對我講大話<br />\n到我踢爆左你之後你一滴眼淚都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4688426d301f3abd2554921064bcba5d628a4f25","tid":42273,"uid":41043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T17:51:29.000Z","msg":"成日鬧交 男朋友都喊<br />\n佢讀drama 有時會以為佢做戲<br />\n但又好真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />